task.summary: Fixed problem with getCurrentContext, changed CtxMain.ctxName to CtxMain.contextName

ContextCreator name changed to ContextConfiguration. ContextCreator and current context are not identified by name anymore, parent is provided as ContextCreator instance. Current context is set from ContextCreator (so noone forget to instantiate used ContextCreator and its partent!). General refactorings.
ContextCreator will throw an exception when attempting to add already existing ID.

Added tests: "UnknownIdException" should "be thrown on attempt to get not existing object" "Child context object" should "be returned when asking for Id overriden by given context" "Parent context object" should "be returned when asking for Id NOT overriden by child context" "Possible youngest context object" should "be returned when asking for given Id"
License added (Simplified BSD), project warnings removed.
Components of lazy objects are initialized lazily, can be obtained using ContextCreator get() method,
scala-di:scala-di maven group:artifact changed to com.lucidmouse.scaladi:scaladi-core
There is new object Context and type setting depending on expected type (in generics way).
Added a few test skeletons for extending multiple contexts. Implementation (both for tests and logic) still to be provided.
Added multiple context extending, hidden some classes. Tests still need to be fixed.
